Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.53,0:44:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.67,0:44:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.11,0:45:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,湿透了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.12,0:45:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.73,0:45:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.21,0:45:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给你弄出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.84,0:46:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这个 这个
