Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.26,1:48:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.39,1:48:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.47,1:48:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.87,1:49:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,被舔了屁眼都变成这样了哦
