Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.95,1:49:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真容易湿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.69,1:49:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.03,1:49:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 自己慢慢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.36,1:49:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样张开 没错..
